cs.AR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) because it focuses on reducing hardware overhead for neural networks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) because it discusses the accuracy of the proposed method on the ImageNet dataset. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it deals with neural networks, and cs.SY (Systems and Control) because it discusses power profiling and area synthesis.
